fulltitle: Mark Crispin Miller, Book Discussion on 'Fooled Again'
title: Mark Crispin Miller, Book Discussion on 'Fooled Again'
_filename: _Mark Crispin Miller, Book Discussion on 'Fooled Again'.mp4
description:
November 27, 2005 | Mr. Crispin-Miller discussed his book Fooled Again: How the Right Stole the 2004 Election and Why They’ll Steal the Next One Too (Unless We Stop Them), published by Basic Books. He discussed presidential politics, voter suppression, and problems with voting machines. Mr. Crispin-Miller responded to questions and comments from viewers.

For more related content, please visit: https://archive.org/details/@altviewstv-fanclub
